* assymetric registration

	1. some restricted people can post to ML

	2. recipients are automatically maintained by fml.

$REJECT_COMMAND_HANDLER = "auto_subscribe" (default automatic
registration) adds a new-comer as both a member who can post to ML and
a recipient. But "auto_asymmetric_regist" provides asymmetric
registration described above.


* configure

% makefml config elena

   MAIN MANU -> 1 -> WHEN_COMMAND_FROM_NOT_MEMBER -> auto_asymmetric_regist

